snippet.title: Punished Props Academy
snippet.description:
Hello! We're Bill & Brittany Doran from Seattle Washington. We build high end replica props and costume from some of your favorite video games, TV shows, movies and more! Follow along with us in our detailed tutorial videos so that you can learn the craft with us!

Punished Props Mission: Transforming passionate fans into confident, skillful makers. Find out more at http://www.punishedprops.com 

Fun ways to help our channel:
Join our Extra Credit Club! https://punishedprops.com/extra-credit-club/
Buy our books! http://www.punishedprops.com/shop

Need to get a hold of us? We rarely check YouTube messages, so please give us a holler on Twitter: https://twitter.com/chinbeard

Follow us on your favorite social media website:
Bill on Twitter: @chinbeard
Facebook: www.facebook.com/punishedprops
Instagram: www.instagram.com/chinbeard

For business inquiries: https://www.punishedprops.com/contact-us/
For customer service support: https://www.punishedprops.com/customer-service/
